Directory structure
===================
   test_4d_qns_general            -- executable
   sim4d_qns_general_input.nml    -- input file (general)
   circle_n63_rayon1_patch0.nml   -- input file (nurbs patches)
   README                         -- info (this file)
   run/                           -- output directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, move into it, and copy nurbs input file
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run
     $ cp ../circle_n63_rayon1_patch0.nml .

1. Run parallel simulation within directory
     $ mpirun -np 4 ../test_4d_qns_general ../sim4d_qns_general_input.nml

2. Run gnuplot scripts generated at runtime
     $ gnuplot --persist rho_split.gnu

